The grand finale of the Fire Conference of the Redeemed Christian Church (RCCG) Prince Of Peace Mega Parish Lagos Province 26, with the theme, ‘Commanding the Year’, holds today. The event will be held at the RCCG Prince of Peace Mega Parish, Lagos Province 26, Araba Baptist Church Street, Ilasamaja, Lagos. The host, Assistant Pastor Babatunde Timothy Akinyeye, said it was necessary people seek the presence of God towards fulfilling their destinies this 2022. 2022: Year Of Crown Of Glory But Pray Against Enemy’s… ‘Over 39.65m MSMEs Operate In Nigeria’ He reminded humanity of the need to live in holiness and peace with all as part of a fulfilled Christian life.